    "description": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >They have taken over everything, it's up to you to LIBERATE the entire world!</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2177230/extras/f8bed9a347dc6f38d5ca3394264c45e6.poster.avif?t=1752091512\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2177230/extras/f8bed9a347dc6f38d5ca3394264c45e6.webm?t=1752091512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2177230/extras/f8bed9a347dc6f38d5ca3394264c45e6.mp4?t=1752091512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>* Find other <strong>Survivors </strong>and bring them with you.<br>* <strong>Build </strong>your base with a Workshop, Generator, Houses and plenty of <strong>Defenses and Traps!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2177230/extras/5eec621f93a09ca8c446b579fe701de8.poster.avif?t=1752091512\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2177230/extras/5eec621f93a09ca8c446b579fe701de8.webm?t=1752091512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2177230/extras/5eec621f93a09ca8c446b579fe701de8.mp4?t=1752091512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>* Split up into <strong>multiple teams</strong> and explore different areas, don't forget to bring <strong>enough ammo</strong> when you leave your base!<br>* Set up outposts to <strong>gather resources </strong>in far away lands and Transport them back to your base through<strong> Automated machines,</strong> ensure the Zombies don't destroy your logistics!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2177230/extras/8be975888169e6d7fd35b9b74ed40179.poster.avif?t=1752091512\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2177230/extras/8be975888169e6d7fd35b9b74ed40179.webm?t=1752091512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2177230/extras/8be975888169e6d7fd35b9b74ed40179.mp4?t=1752091512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>* <strong>Craft items</strong>, armor, weapons and lots of ammo, build <strong>Drones</strong> to help you <strong>Gather, Craft and Patrol</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2177230/extras/8c9911b4d0b05a4ca685aaccaf4e1eab.poster.avif?t=1752091512\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2177230/extras/8c9911b4d0b05a4ca685aaccaf4e1eab.webm?t=1752091512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2177230/extras/8c9911b4d0b05a4ca685aaccaf4e1eab.mp4?t=1752091512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>* Explore a large <strong>persistent open world</strong>, with no loading or mission instances, everything happens in the world.<br>* Turn-Based so you can take your time to think and come up with the <strong>perfect Strategy</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2177230/extras/c8bca05080155ebd7ea0293d2a6c809b.poster.avif?t=1752091512\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2177230/extras/c8bca05080155ebd7ea0293d2a6c809b.webm?t=1752091512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2177230/extras/c8bca05080155ebd7ea0293d2a6c809b.mp4?t=1752091512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>* <strong>Ambush</strong> Zombies and take them all out without suffering casualties<br>* Be careful when exploring at <strong>night</strong>, and be even more careful so you don't attract a <strong>massive horde!</strong><br><br>Start just with <strong>one</strong> Survivor and <strong>Liberate the entire World!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Add to your Wishlist now! 2025</h2><br><strong>And follow the Development on YouTube @CodeMonkeyUnity</strong>",
